	<div style="padding-bottom:10px;"><img alt="Striped: from left, Daniel Rella, Chris Couri and Tom Darrow." src="//assets.entrepreneur.com/article/all-lined-up-and-in-the-paint.jpg" /><br />
<div style="font-size:11px; color:#333; line-height:12px; padding:5px 0 5px 0; text-align:right; width:475px;">Striped: from left, Daniel Rella, Chris Couri and Tom Darrow.<br />
